CaFE only requires Frama-C, so start by installing Frama-C from the sources or
from OPAM.

OPAM 
     
     Install the opam packet manager, then 'opam install frama-c'

From the sources
     
     You can download Frama-C in http://frama-c.com/

Once Frama-C is installed : 

     autoconf
     ./configure
     make depend
     make
     sudo make install
     
     (Optionnal, will print the options and check if it is well installed) 
     frama-c -cafe-h
     